            "header": "Seat reservation required on trains to and from Hamburg from 26 June to 16 August",
            "body": "From 26 June to 16 August, a seat reservation is required on journeys between Denmark and Hamburg on ECE trains \u2013 including local journeys. This is due to the high number of travellers during the summer period. You can find more information about seat reservations on dsb.dk",
